 "lines": [
  {
   "i": 1,
   "en": "Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 2,
   "en": "So today, there's a character show"
  },
  {
   "i": 3,
   "en": "here in this arcade"
  },
  {
   "i": 4,
   "en": "Ozaki"
  },
  {
   "i": 5,
   "en": "That's right. And you'll be playing"
  },
  {
   "i": 6,
   "en": "an original heroine, Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 7,
   "en": "Your character's name is..."
  },
  {
   "i": 8,
   "en": "'Transforming Fairy Ellie'!"
  },
  {
   "i": 9,
   "en": "Kind of silly?"
  },
  {
   "i": 10,
   "en": "It is. I think so too, but"
  },
  {
   "i": 11,
   "en": "it's what the client ordered..."
  },
  {
   "i": 12,
   "en": "Let's stay positive about it"
  },
  {
   "i": 13,
   "en": "Aim for a TV series?"
  },
  {
   "i": 14,
   "en": "That's... probably not happening"
  },
  {
   "i": 15,
   "en": "Why not?"
  },
  {
   "i": 16,
   "en": "She's an instant character,"
  },
  {
   "i": 17,
   "en": "invented just for today"
  },
  {
   "i": 18,
   "en": "No big dreams. Just do the job right"
  },
  {
   "i": 19,
   "en": "That's so cool"
  },
  {
   "i": 20,
   "en": "You... honestly think so?"
  },
  {
   "i": 21,
   "en": "Yeah..."
  },
  {
   "i": 22,
   "en": "Then you may want to polish your"
  },
  {
   "i": 23,
   "en": "taste a little. For your own good"
  },
  {
   "i": 24,
   "en": "Really?"
  },
  {
   "i": 25,
   "en": "Well, fine. A job's a job."
  },
  {
   "i": 26,
   "en": "Let's do it properly"
  },
  {
   "i": 27,
   "en": "A quick rehearsal before the show?"
  },
  {
   "i": 28,
   "en": "Okay"
  },
  {
   "i": 29,
   "en": "I'll play the villain for you"
  },
  {
   "i": 30,
   "en": "Okay. Then I'm the heroine."
  },
  {
   "i": 31,
   "en": "And... action!"
  },
  {
   "i": 32,
   "en": "Ufufufufu! Found you, Ellie!"
  },
  {
   "i": 33,
   "en": "Ah! The evil fairy, Ozakiller!"
  },
  {
   "i": 34,
   "en": "Not transformed yet, I see. Then―㌍"
  },
  {
   "i": 35,
   "en": "I'll crush you before you power up!"
  },
  {
   "i": 36,
   "en": "I won't let you."
  },
  {
   "i": 37,
   "en": "You'll pay for what you did!"
  },
  {
   "i": 38,
   "en": "Oh my, whatever do you mean?"
  },
  {
   "i": 39,
   "en": "What evil have I ever done?"
  },
  {
   "i": 40,
   "en": "Littering! You thought no one"
  },
  {
   "i": 41,
   "en": "was watching, didn't you?"
  },
  {
   "i": 42,
   "en": "Ngh... you SAW that..."
  },
  {
   "i": 43,
   "en": "Fufufu! But dirtying"
  },
  {
   "i": 44,
   "en": "this Earth is my job♪"
  },
  {
   "i": 45,
   "en": "And I won't allow it!"
  },
  {
   "i": 46,
   "en": "...Yes, that's the spirit, Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 47,
   "en": "You skipped my lunch!"
  },
  {
   "i": 48,
   "en": "Huh? Your... lunch?"
  },
  {
   "i": 49,
   "en": "Yes! That day at the office with all"
  },
  {
   "i": 50,
   "en": "the paperwork... you skipped it!"
  },
  {
   "i": 51,
   "en": "Eri, that... that actually happened"
  },
  {
   "i": 52,
   "en": "You can't bring real life into a show"
  },
  {
   "i": 53,
   "en": "Ah... I'm sorry"
  },
  {
   "i": 54,
   "en": "You made me do lessons!"
  },
  {
   "i": 55,
   "en": "Huh...? Lessons?"
  },
  {
   "i": 56,
   "en": "Voice and dance lessons! So many,"
  },
  {
   "i": 57,
   "en": "even when I was tired!"
  },
  {
   "i": 58,
   "en": "E-Eri... don't tell me you actually"
  },
  {
   "i": 59,
   "en": "resent me for that?"
  },
  {
   "i": 60,
   "en": "...No. Just trying it out"
  },
  {
   "i": 61,
   "en": "Haah, don't scare me like that"
  },
  {
   "i": 62,
   "en": "Besides, you can't bring real life"
  },
  {
   "i": 63,
   "en": "into a show, right?"
  },
  {
   "i": 64,
   "en": "...I'm sorry"
  },
  {
   "i": 65,
   "en": "Well, fine."
  },
  {
   "i": 66,
   "en": "It's only rehearsal"
  },
  {
   "i": 67,
   "en": "Now, here's your big moment!"
  },
  {
   "i": 68,
   "en": "Show me your transformation!"
  },
  {
   "i": 69,
   "en": "How do I transform?"
  },
  {
   "i": 70,
   "en": "Just like the script says: spin the"
  },
  {
   "i": 71,
   "en": "wand at the upper right of your head"
  },
  {
   "i": 72,
   "en": "Upper right..."
  },
  {
   "i": 73,
   "en": "Fast as you can, in a clean circle"
  },
  {
   "i": 74,
   "en": "Got it"
  },
  {
   "i": 75,
   "en": "...All right... transform!"
  },
  {
   "i": 76,
   "en": "Chaaange! Transforming Fairy Ellie!"
  },
  {
   "i": 77,
   "en": "...Was that okay?"
  },
  {
   "i": 78,
   "en": "Yes, you nailed it"
  },
  {
   "i": 79,
   "en": "In the real show, once that move ends,"
  },
  {
   "i": 80,
   "en": "duck backstage and change"
  },
  {
   "i": 81,
   "en": "I'd say you're ready."
  },
  {
   "i": 82,
   "en": "Keep it up in the real thing"
  },
  {
   "i": 83,
   "en": "Okay!"
  },
  {
   "i": 84,
   "en": "She praised me! Playing Fairy Ellie"
  },
  {
   "i": 85,
   "en": "might actually be fun!"
  },
  {
   "i": 86,
   "en": "Hooold it right there!"
  },
  {
   "i": 87,
   "en": "Huh?"
  },
  {
   "i": 88,
   "en": "That's wrong, Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 89,
   "en": "I said upper RIGHT."
  },
  {
   "i": 90,
   "en": "That's your left"
  },
  {
   "i": 91,
   "en": "......Ah"
  },
  {
   "i": 92,
   "en": "What do I become if I spin upper left?"
  },
  {
   "i": 93,
   "en": "Who knows..."
  },
  {
   "i": 94,
   "en": "Mean-spirited Black Ellie?"
  },
  {
   "i": 95,
   "en": "...Let's not invent new heroines"
  },
  {
   "i": 96,
   "en": "on your own, please"
  },
  {
   "i": 97,
   "en": "Combining robot 'Great Ellie' appears?"
  },
  {
   "i": 98,
   "en": "We don't have effects that fancy."
  },
  {
   "i": 99,
   "en": "This isn't a theme-park show"
  },
  {
   "i": 100,
   "en": "Anyway, no mixing them up on stage"
  },
  {
   "i": 101,
   "en": "...Okay"
  },
  {
   "i": 102,
   "en": "She scolded me a little. Even though"
  },
  {
   "i": 103,
   "en": "the audience would never notice..."
  },
  {
   "i": 104,
   "en": "Ummm... not like this..."
  },
  {
   "i": 105,
   "en": "not like that either..."
  },
  {
   "i": 106,
   "en": "........"
  },
  {
   "i": 107,
   "en": "Prepare yourself, Ellie!"
  },
  {
   "i": 108,
   "en": "KYEEEEEEEH!!"
  },
  {
   "i": 109,
   "en": "Hyah?! Uh... uhhhh..."
  },
  {
   "i": 110,
   "en": "Game over, I'd say"
  },
  {
   "i": 111,
   "en": "Uh... uuugh..."
  },
  {
   "i": 112,
   "en": "Flub your transformation and the"
  },
  {
   "i": 113,
   "en": "villain gets you, just like that"
  },
  {
   "i": 114,
   "en": "R-Right...."
  },
  {
   "i": 115,
   "en": "Transforming is hard..."
  },
  {
   "i": 116,
   "en": "Want to practice once more?"
  },
  {
   "i": 117,
   "en": "From the top, then"
  },
  {
   "i": 118,
   "en": "Back to square one."
  },
  {
   "i": 119,
   "en": "This might take a while to learn"
  }
 ]
